author: @underratedgroupsneedslove6194
text:
GUYS ! 
*TWICE* defeated the Zombie invasion in *"Like Ooh Ahh"* ... As you may all know, TWICE are as sweet and tasteful as apples. So sweet, that the girls decided to throw a huge celebration in order to cheer up everyone who had lost their close/loved ones in the Zombie Apocalypse. Hence releasing *"Cheer Up"* . After the huge celebration, the girls went home ...  WAIT ! Apparently demons and villains rises onto the Earth's surface from the Underworld. Once again, the lovely TWICE have to save the world again. So they're pretty bummed fighting demons and villains in *"TT"* ... They're pretty tired. But in the end, they end up victorious (did you ever doubt? Haha). They finally got to go home. The next morning (3am), the lovely TWICE woke up from loud banging and knocking on their door, *"Knock Knock"* . A villager told the girls, "Alien Invasion". Ohhh boi. The girls are long overdue for a proper goodnight sleep. ... Another day, another fight with Aliens in *"Signal"* , and no sleep. 
They seemed to realize this ... This hard life, would never end. So they comeback with *"Once Begins"* = Once 'again, it' begins
